content: Hey there! Trans woman from Illinois looking to setup a 24-hour donation and registration drive themed around the Harris-Walz campaign! I know how to stream on Twitch so that's not a big deal but how would I make sure I'm "above board"? Like are there specific places I should be linking to for donations and registrations?
Hello, KutieKatelyn! Thank you so much for setting this up! You can direct people to donate at: kamalaharris.com/donate

I figured that'd be okay but I didn't know if there was anything specific I should do! 

Now I need to figure out how to get the tracker working <:CZthink:1117262503072759838>
Also thank you for answering ðŸ§¡
The party's website for voting is https://iwillvote.com
Absolutely! feel free to ping any of us mods, anytime. I can't guarantee we will all be on, but we are here to help!
Once I get more details, where would be a good place to discuss or share it? <:peek:1182065990033473577>
You can share with your circle! On this site we can't share any non-official fundraising. That's a big one for us as it's campaign finance law
Didn't know if grassroots stuff was cool to share here with one another so good to know!
It's great that you are doing this! And, yeah, it's against the law for us to allow the sharing of non-official fundraising on this server
Well we have a saying in the LGBT community: "Be gay, do crime"

In Animal Crossing, I assume that [Biden HQ's island](https://www.polygon.com/2020/10/16/21519632/joe-biden-animal-crossing-island-dream-code-merch-signs-shirts-swag) has been remodeled for Kamala.  In Fortnite, there was a BBB custom map.  Since Reach has rankings, I also think it's gamified.
